revision.text: ==Yankunytjatjara== ===Noun=== {{head|kdd|verb form}} # [[nominal|Nominal]] form of the corresponding verb; [[going]]. ====Usage notes==== * The word '''yankunytja''' is one of the distinguishing features of Yankunytjatjara. For example, the word [[Yankunytjatjara]] literally means "having-'''yankunytja'''". ===References=== * {{R:Goddard 1992|}}
